{"type":"message","id":"6d491d47","parentId":"1eb38686","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:50:18.740Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p2bzcvwuonkb_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 004916\r\n\r\n## Applied Mutations\r\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\r\nRejected: the (missing)\r\n\r\n## LLM Response\r\n<think>\r\nLooking at my current state and goals:\r\n\r\n1. Phase 0 COMPLETE - Sandbox foundation established\r\n2. Phase 1 COMPLETE - Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\r\n3. Key insight: Compression-Causal Duality - causal structure IS invariant structure\r\n4. Next action: Implement TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) classifier\r\n\r\nThe pending TIC experiment requires:\r\n- Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n- Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- Predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n- Validate against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\r\n\r\nI need to create a script that:\r\n1. Reads recent pulse logs (last 20)\r\n2. Implements TIC classifier to identify invariants vs variants\r\n3. Tests next-pulse prediction accuracy\r\n\r\nLet me look at what files exist:\r\n- research/ARCHITECTURE-COMPARISON.md\r\n- research/GAP-DECAY-MAPPING.md\r\n- research/COMPRESSION-CAUSAL-DUALITY.md\r\n- logs/pulse_*.md files\r\n\r\nI should create a TIC experiment script. Let me check what pulse logs exist and create the experiment.\r\n\r\nFirst, I need to understand the pulse log format. Looking at the recent pulse mentioned: pulse_2026-03-24 004715.md\r\n\r\nLet me create the TIC experiment implementation.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariants vs variants across recent pulse logs and tests next-pulse prediction.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate the TIC experiment script that analyzes last 20 pulse logs, classifies invariant/variant content, and tests prediction accuracy against success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction).\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # TIC Experiment: Temporal Invariance Compression\r\n# Validates: Causal structure = Invariant structure hypothesis\r\n# Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$lookback = 20,\r\n    [string]$logDir = \"logs\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n$startTime = Get-Date\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Experiment: Temporal Invariance Compression ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Lookback: $lookback pulses\"\r\nWrite-Host \"Started: $startTime\"\r\nWrite-Host \"\"\r\n\r\n# Collect pulse logs\r\n$pulseFiles = Get-ChildItem -Path $logDir -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | \r\n    Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | \r\n    Select-Object -First $lookback\r\n\r\nif ($pulseFiles.Count -lt 3) {\r\n    Write-Host \"ERROR: Need at least 3 pulses for TIC experiment\" -ForegroundColor Red\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Collected $($pulseFiles.Count) pulse logs\"\r\n\r\n# Parse pulse content - extract key elements\r\nfunction Parse-PulseContent {\r\n    param([string]$content)\r\n    \r\n    $elements = @{\r\n        Goals = @()\r\n        Actions = @()\r\n        Mutations = @()\r\n        Observations = @()\r\n        Timestamp = $null\r\n        RawContent = $content\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract goal references\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)## Goals:.*?(?=##|\\z)') {\r\n        $elements.Goals = [regex]::Matches($_.Value, '- \\[ \\] (.+)') | ForEach-Object { $_.Groups[1].Value }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract mutation files\r\n    $mutationMatches = [regex]::Matches($content, 'file: (.+\\.md|\\S+\\.ps1|\\S+\\.json)')\r\n    $elements.Mutations = $mutationMatches | ForEach-Object { $_.Groups[1].Value }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract action keywords\r\n    $actionWords = @('Create', 'Update', 'Delete', 'Implement', 'Test', 'Analyze', 'Define', 'Tune', 'Wire', 'Measure')\r\n    foreach ($word in $actionWords) {\r\n        if ($content -match $word) {\r\n            $elements.Actions += $word\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract observations\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)### OBSERVATION\\s*(.+?)(?=###|\\z)') {\r\n        $elements.Observations += $matches[1].Trim()\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $elements\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Load all pulse data\r\n$pulseData = @()\r\nforeach ($file in $pulseFiles) {\r\n    $content = Get-Content $file.FullName -Raw\r\n    $pulseData += @{\r\n        File = $file.Name\r\n        Timestamp = $file.LastWriteTime\r\n        Content = $content\r\n        Elements = Parse-PulseContent $content\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Parsed pulse contents\"\r\n\r\n# === INVARIANT DETECTION ===\r\n# Invariants: patterns that persist across multiple pulses\r\n# Variants: patterns that appear in one pulse only\r\n\r\n$invariantPatterns = @{\r\n    Goals = @{}\r\n    Actions = @{}\r\n    Mutations = @{}\r\n}\r\n\r\n$variantPatterns = @{\r\n    Goals = @()\r\n    Actions = @()\r\n    Mutations = @()\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Count goal persistence\r\nforeach ($pulse in $pulseData) {\r\n    foreach ($goal in $pulse.Elements.Goals) {\r\n        if ($invariantPatterns.Goals.ContainsKey($goal)) {\r\n            $invariantPatterns.Goals[$goal]++\r\n        } else {\r\n            $invariantPatterns.Goals[$goal] = 1\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($action in $pulse.Elements.Actions) {\r\n        if ($invariantPatterns.Actions.ContainsKey($action)) {\r\n            $invariantPatterns.Actions[$action]++\r\n        } else {\r\n            $invariant\r\n\r\n## For Next Instantiation\r\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\r\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 00:49:38"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1308,"aggregated":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 004916\r\n\r\n## Applied Mutations\r\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\r\nRejected: the (missing)\r\n\r\n## LLM Response\r\n<think>\r\nLooking at my current state and goals:\r\n\r\n1. Phase 0 COMPLETE - Sandbox foundation established\r\n2. Phase 1 COMPLETE - Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\r\n3. Key insight: Compression-Causal Duality - causal structure IS invariant structure\r\n4. Next action: Implement TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) classifier\r\n\r\nThe pending TIC experiment requires:\r\n- Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n- Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- Predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n- Validate against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\r\n\r\nI need to create a script that:\r\n1. Reads recent pulse logs (last 20)\r\n2. Implements TIC classifier to identify invariants vs variants\r\n3. Tests next-pulse prediction accuracy\r\n\r\nLet me look at what files exist:\r\n- research/ARCHITECTURE-COMPARISON.md\r\n- research/GAP-DECAY-MAPPING.md\r\n- research/COMPRESSION-CAUSAL-DUALITY.md\r\n- logs/pulse_*.md files\r\n\r\nI should create a TIC experiment script. Let me check what pulse logs exist and create the experiment.\r\n\r\nFirst, I need to understand the pulse log format. Looking at the recent pulse mentioned: pulse_2026-03-24 004715.md\r\n\r\nLet me create the TIC experiment implementation.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariants vs variants across recent pulse logs and tests next-pulse prediction.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate the TIC experiment script that analyzes last 20 pulse logs, classifies invariant/variant content, and tests prediction accuracy against success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction).\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # TIC Experiment: Temporal Invariance Compression\r\n# Validates: Causal structure = Invariant structure hypothesis\r\n# Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$lookback = 20,\r\n    [string]$logDir = \"logs\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n$startTime = Get-Date\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Experiment: Temporal Invariance Compression ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Lookback: $lookback pulses\"\r\nWrite-Host \"Started: $startTime\"\r\nWrite-Host \"\"\r\n\r\n# Collect pulse logs\r\n$pulseFiles = Get-ChildItem -Path $logDir -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | \r\n    Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | \r\n    Select-Object -First $lookback\r\n\r\nif ($pulseFiles.Count -lt 3) {\r\n    Write-Host \"ERROR: Need at least 3 pulses for TIC experiment\" -ForegroundColor Red\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Collected $($pulseFiles.Count) pulse logs\"\r\n\r\n# Parse pulse content - extract key elements\r\nfunction Parse-PulseContent {\r\n    param([string]$content)\r\n    \r\n    $elements = @{\r\n        Goals = @()\r\n        Actions = @()\r\n        Mutations = @()\r\n        Observations = @()\r\n        Timestamp = $null\r\n        RawContent = $content\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract goal references\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)## Goals:.*?(?=##|\\z)') {\r\n        $elements.Goals = [regex]::Matches($_.Value, '- \\[ \\] (.+)') | ForEach-Object { $_.Groups[1].Value }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract mutation files\r\n    $mutationMatches = [regex]::Matches($content, 'file: (.+\\.md|\\S+\\.ps1|\\S+\\.json)')\r\n    $elements.Mutations = $mutationMatches | ForEach-Object { $_.Groups[1].Value }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract action keywords\r\n    $actionWords = @('Create', 'Update', 'Delete', 'Implement', 'Test', 'Analyze', 'Define', 'Tune', 'Wire', 'Measure')\r\n    foreach ($word in $actionWords) {\r\n        if ($content -match $word) {\r\n            $elements.Actions += $word\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract observations\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)### OBSERVATION\\s*(.+?)(?=###|\\z)') {\r\n        $elements.Observations += $matches[1].Trim()\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $elements\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Load all pulse data\r\n$pulseData = @()\r\nforeach ($file in $pulseFiles) {\r\n    $content = Get-Content $file.FullName -Raw\r\n    $pulseData += @{\r\n        File = $file.Name\r\n        Timestamp = $file.LastWriteTime\r\n        Content = $content\r\n        Elements = Parse-PulseContent $content\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Parsed pulse contents\"\r\n\r\n# === INVARIANT DETECTION ===\r\n# Invariants: patterns that persist across multiple pulses\r\n# Variants: patterns that appear in one pulse only\r\n\r\n$invariantPatterns = @{\r\n    Goals = @{}\r\n    Actions = @{}\r\n    Mutations = @{}\r\n}\r\n\r\n$variantPatterns = @{\r\n    Goals = @()\r\n    Actions = @()\r\n    Mutations = @()\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Count goal persistence\r\nforeach ($pulse in $pulseData) {\r\n    foreach ($goal in $pulse.Elements.Goals) {\r\n        if ($invariantPatterns.Goals.ContainsKey($goal)) {\r\n            $invariantPatterns.Goals[$goal]++\r\n        } else {\r\n            $invariantPatterns.Goals[$goal] = 1\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($action in $pulse.Elements.Actions) {\r\n        if ($invariantPatterns.Actions.ContainsKey($action)) {\r\n            $invariantPatterns.Actions[$action]++\r\n        } else {\r\n            $invariant\r\n\r\n## For Next Instantiation\r\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\r\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 00:49:38","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774327818737}}
